title: Disney Karaok Collection CDG+MP3 2 Discs
description:
2 CDs of Disney Karaoke songs

These are CDG + MP3 files.  They are to be burned to disc to play on an image based karaoke machine or to play on PC via VLC player.

They are sourced from differing locations (even made a few myself with karaoke creator programme)
